short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Vocaire is a platform that helps physical therapists with their admin work

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Vocaire Chrome extension is a practical tool designed exclusively for physical therapists. Seamlessly integrated with your Vocaire account, this extension significantly simplifies your admin work by automating the journaling process. Install the Vocaire Chrome extension to access Vocaie's features from your EHR! Note: A Vocaire account is required to utilize this extension's features.
